        Strata Title vs Torrens Title in Queensland: What Sellers Need to Know
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        The title type attached to your property shapes the entire transaction, from what you disclose to how buyers assess value. Here is what the difference means in practice.
      </p>
